{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6964a7ca71","title":"“右派”诗","origin":"《山东文艺界反右派斗争文集》，山东人民出版社，一九五九年济南。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"07660b7377","index":0,"year":1957,"month":7,"day":18,"articleId":"6964a7ca71"}],"tags":[{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"b22a936287","name":"山东"},{"id":"bcc43a353f","name":"王希坚"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"aa49787520","type":"title","text":"“右派”诗","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6964a7ca71"},{"id":"db0e55a330","type":"authors","text":"山东王希坚","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6964a7ca71"},{"id":"395c3af386","type":"subtitle","text":"王希坚的“右派”诗","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6964a7ca71"},{"id":"99a2d7764b","type":"paragraph","text":"十年一瞬去如流","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6964a7ca71"},{"id":"c9e8601f3e","type":"paragraph","text":"惭愧席间强应酬","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6964a7ca71"},{"id":"949ce52d2c","type":"paragraph","text":"莫怨寒风吹落叶","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6964a7ca71"},{"id":"6447ca7e1a","type":"paragraph","text":"且教稚子认牵牛","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6964a7ca71"},{"id":"329f37a345","type":"paragraph","text":" 1957．7．18","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6964a7ca71"},{"id":"d15c685918","type":"paragraph","text":"按：王希坚在检讨中说：“这首诗把轰轰烈烈的反右派斗争比作寒风吹落叶，对自己的过去感到惭愧，对将来感到惶惑。”可以看出王希坚反党不成的失望情绪。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6964a7ca71"},{"id":"6af36f88e6","type":"paragraph","text":"朝辞白帝彩云间","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6964a7ca71"},{"id":"6c88419b8b","type":"paragraph","text":"千里江陵不见还","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6964a7ca71"},{"id":"27b471e284","type":"paragraph","text":"两岸猿声啼不住","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6964a7ca71"},{"id":"93899a2172","type":"paragraph","text":"轻舟已在水中翻","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6964a7ca71"},{"id":"3b9077adf1","type":"paragraph","text":" 1957．8．27","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6964a7ca71"},{"id":"5f8bf631ab","type":"paragraph","text":"按：这是借用我国唐代大诗人李白的“下江陵”一诗，并加以改动来表达王希坚自己的情绪的。原诗是：“朝辞白帝彩云间，千里江陵一日还，两岸猿声啼不住，轻舟已过万重山。”王希坚在这里把“一日还”改为“不见还”，把“已过万重山”改为“已在水中飜”。意思是说：反右派中在众目睽睽之下王希坚自己感到过去一切一去不复返了。他的这只船已在水中翻了。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6964a7ca71"},{"id":"58bc780bd6","type":"paragraph","text":"闲爱孤云静爱僧","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6964a7ca71"},{"id":"e05bcb43f2","type":"paragraph","text":"君应着意爱浮萍","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6964a7ca71"},{"id":"9e6c3881dd","type":"paragraph","text":"随风逐浪团团转","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6964a7ca71"},{"id":"bc36a0d667","type":"paragraph","text":"永不生根入土中","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6964a7ca71"},{"id":"979e92ca00","type":"paragraph","text":" 1957．7．19","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6964a7ca71"},{"id":"bbca75d44b","type":"paragraph","text":"(题名“赠某人”)","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6964a7ca71"},{"id":"58e8a5b6ed","type":"paragraph","text":"按：王希坚虽然对自己感到了悲观和失望，但是大家对他的批判他仍不服。在这首诗里，他对在反右派斗争中站起来批判他的同志，进行了恶毒的诬骂，说这些同志没有主见，随风逐流。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6964a7ca71"},{"id":"aff7d74e12","type":"paragraph","text":"可笑王希坚","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6964a7ca71"},{"id":"5df59de87c","type":"paragraph","text":"胆大要包天","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6964a7ca71"},{"id":"fbb9950e9c","type":"paragraph","text":"想去文艺界","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6964a7ca71"},{"id":"66bbb59090","type":"paragraph","text":"夺取领导权","index"